Xasha, because of the new spell the 50+ firepets cast, Shielding, it and Burnout 3 (our pants, and most mages til they stumble across Burnout 4) are mutually exclusive. Someone posted that earlier. The AC components do not stack if in the same affect slot. By moving the AC component in the Burnout series to another slot, it permits them to stack appropriately.<br>
<br>
